Compass RE Texas, LLC - Lake Conroe

data.description: Beautiful 1 story custom home in the Lake Community of Walden. Great curb appeal as this home sits on large corner lot. This home features 3 bedrooms 2.5 baths, 3 car garage. Welcoming entry way with high ceilings, crown molding, corner fireplace in living room, large windows in living and dining area. Island kitchen with gas cook top, granite countertops with an abundance of cabinets for storage and walk in pantry, breakfast bar and breakfast room all open to living room. Primary bedroom with high ceilings, primary bath with walk in shower, double sinks and large walk in closet. Study can also be used as a 4th bedroom. Covered back patio, fenced. Home is conveniently located within walking distance to fitness, tennis and Racquetball center. Also nearby is Yacht club, swimming pools, golf club and Marina. Perfect place to launch your boat and explore Lake Conroe
